Why do you have to get to a point where
something's going to be taken from you

794
01:04:21,600 --> 01:04:24,101
for you to realize how important it is?

795
01:04:24,760 --> 01:04:27,067
No need to explain. I know you love her.

796
01:04:28,320 --> 01:04:29,706
Yeah.

797
01:04:33,440 --> 01:04:34,780
Yeah.

798
01:05:11,480 --> 01:05:13,264
Did you hear that?

799
