Let's keep going.

805
01:08:03,840 --> 01:08:05,544
Hi, sweetie.

806
01:08:06,160 --> 01:08:07,625
Hey.

807
01:08:08,520 --> 01:08:10,110
I'm right here.

808
01:08:11,240 --> 01:08:12,910
I'm right here.

809
01:08:16,360 --> 01:08:18,383
Are you still hurting?

810
01:08:20,520 --> 01:08:22,782
